document: Introduction to AI: Core concepts and applications; practical labs and projects.
Data Structures: Abstract data types, trees, graphs, and algorithmic analysis.
Web Development: Frontend and backend fundamentals; REST APIs and deployment.
Machine Learning: Supervised and unsupervised learning; model evaluation.
Operating Systems: Processes, memory, scheduling, and concurrency basics.
Database Systems: Relational modeling, SQL, indexing, and transactions.
Computer Networks: OSI model, routing, switching, and network security.
Software Architecture: Requirements, design patterns, testing, and CI/CD.
Cybersecurity: Threat models, cryptography basics, and secure coding.
Cloud Computing: Virtualization, containerization, and distributed systems.
